long_description: some clients wish to come less often, usually every other week, however we believe that weekly therapy is the most effective strategy . we see our job as partnering with you to actualize those things, while helping you overcome the obstacles that get in your way. beyond symptom relief, we strive to help you make use of your personal history to grow and move forward, overcome unproductive habits, uncover and deal with emotional stuck points, and ultimately improve self-worth, relationships, and work fulfilment.

generated_description: frazier & frazier counseling is a private practice that offers psychotherapy services for adults, children, adolescents, and families of all ages. the company is run by a husband and wife team, barbara frazier and her husband, who have over 40 years of experience in private practice and 17 years of expertise in child abuse protection and prevention. they provide individual psychotherapy sessions on a weekly basis, with a focus on helping clients overcome emotional stuck points, overcome unproductive habits, and improve self-worth, relationships, and work fulfillment. the first session is conducted with parents alone to gain a thorough understanding of the problems and issues of concern before seeing the child. they also offer adolescent psychotherapy and couples/marital counseling.
